| Concept                 | Formula                              | Purpose               |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------ | --------------------- |
| Quartile Deviation (QD) | $(Q_3 - Q_1)/2$                      | Spread of middle 50%  |
| Coefficient of QD       | $(Q_3 - Q_1)/(Q_3 + Q_1)$            | Comparison (relative) |
| Sensitive to extremes?  | **No**                               | Better than Range     |
| Best for                | Income, Biological data, Skewed data |                       |
